{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": \"count\", \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001", "id": "msg_014DAk8jJZPbVQKUiigEjxT5", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I"}], "stop_reason": "max_tokens", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 551, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 1, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Warmup\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929", "id": "msg_012BS1aHYHjqjx3BgF5tPiww", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I'm ready to help! I'm Claude Code, Anthropic's CLI assistant specialized in exploring codebases and designing implementation plans.\n\nI understand that I'm in **READ-ONLY mode** - I can explore the codebase and create plans, but I cannot create, modify, or delete any files.\n\nLet me check what we're working with:\n\n<function_calls>\n<invoke name=\"bash\">\n<parameter name=\"command\">cd /code && pwd</parameter>\n</invoke>\n</function_calls>\n<invoke name=\"read_file\">\n<parameter name=\"path\">/code</parameter>\n</invoke>\n<function_calls>\n<invoke name=\"bash\">\n<parameter name=\"command\">cd /code && ls -la</parameter>\n</invoke>\n</function_calls>\n<invoke name=\"bash\">\n<parameter name=\"command\">cd /code && find . -type f -name \"*.py\" -o -name \"*.js\" -o -name \"*.ts\" -o -name \"*.json\" -o -name \"*.md\" | head -20</parameter>\n</invoke>\n\nI'm warmed up and ready to explore your codebase! What requirements or feature would you like me to analyze and design an implementation plan for?"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 950, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 346, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"This is a test message: 'Knock knock!'\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929", "id": "msg_017yyiSw6ta7vSsSrtQBQ4hB", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Knock knock! Who's there? \ud83d\ude0a\n\nIs there anything you'd like me to help you with? I can assist with:\n- Writing or modifying code\n- Fixing bugs\n- Exploring your codebase\n- Answering questions about your code\n- Running tests or builds\n- Creating commits or pull requests\n\nJust let me know what you need!"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 3, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 18847, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 83, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"This is a test message: 'Knock knock!'\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}, {\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Knock knock! Who's there? \\ud83d\\ude0a\\n\\nIs there anything you'd like me to help you with? I can assist with:\\n- Writing or modifying code\\n- Fixing bugs\\n- Exploring your codebase\\n- Answering questions about your code\\n- Running tests or builds\\n- Creating commits or pull requests\\n\\nJust let me know what you need!\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"assistant\"}, {\"content\": [{\"text\": \"This is a follow-up test message. 'Amos.'\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929", "id": "msg_01SKHvGX4zuVw2YjGk88j7YF", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Amos who? \ud83d\ude04\n\nI'm ready to help whenever you need! Feel free to ask me to work on any coding tasks, investigate issues, or explore your repository."}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 3, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 101, "cache_read_input_tokens": 18847, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 101, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 41, "service_tier": "standard"}, "context_management": {"applied_edits": []}}}
